<subSubSection pageId="81" pageNumber="82" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="81.[151,1436,1700,1797]" pageId="81" pageNumber="82">
We group tentatively in this assemblage some southern African species of the 
<emphasis box="[1092,1234,1701,1724]" italics="true" pageId="81" pageNumber="82">Mesocutatus</emphasis>
lineage with ten antennomeres as 
<taxonomicName authority="(Olivier, 1811)" authorityName="Olivier" authorityYear="1811" baseAuthorityName="Olivier" baseAuthorityYear="1811" box="[351,677,1735,1760]" class="Insecta" family="Meloidae" genus="Hycleus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="81" pageNumber="82" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="africanus">
<emphasis box="[351,495,1736,1760]" italics="true" pageId="81" pageNumber="82">H. africanus</emphasis>
(Olivier, 1811)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Peringuey, 1909)" authorityName="Bologna &amp; Amore &amp; Pitzalis" authorityYear="2018" baseAuthorityName="Peringuey" baseAuthorityYear="1909" box="[693,1061,1735,1760]" class="Insecta" family="Meloidae" genus="Hycleus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="81" pageNumber="82" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="namaquus">
<emphasis box="[693,846,1737,1760]" italics="true" pageId="81" pageNumber="82">H. namaquus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Peringuey" box="[864,1053,1735,1760]" pageId="81" pageNumber="82" refString="Peringuey, L. (1909) Descriptive catalogue of the Coleoptera of South Africa Family Meloidae. Transactions of the Royal Society of South Africa, 1, 165 - 297, 4 pls." type="journal article" year="1909">Péringuey, 1909</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="(Wulfen, 1786)" authorityName="Wulfen" authorityYear="1786" baseAuthorityName="Wulfen" baseAuthorityYear="1786" class="Insecta" family="Meloidae" genus="Hycleus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="81" pageNumber="82" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadriguttatus">
<emphasis box="[1123,1326,1736,1760]" italics="true" pageId="81" pageNumber="82">H. quadriguttatus</emphasis>
